query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(k mk t) NoHashJoin(k mk t ci) NoNestLoop(ci k mk t n) */ select min(k.keyword) AS movie_keyword,
min(n.name) AS actor_name,
min(t.title) AS hero_movie
from keyword AS k
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('superhero',
'fight',
'based-on-novel',
'laser',
'based-on-comic',
'tv-special',
'marvel-comics',
'tv-special')
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2003
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
inner join name AS n
on n.id = ci.person_id;
